lead_paragraph: Alfredo Simon knew the best thing he could do for Cincinnati's historically bad bullpen was to stay in the game a long time. He accomplished his goal, but the relievers still had trouble.

headline.print_headline: Reds Beat Brewers 9-5 Despite Bullpen Extending Bad Streak
